stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Moving: start()
    Moving --> AwaitingDetail: camera reaches stop
    AwaitingDetail --> Moving: detail closes and stops remain
    AwaitingDetail --> Complete: final detail closes
    Moving --> Idle: stop()
    AwaitingDetail --> Idle: stop()
    Complete --> FreeExploration: credits close
